description: In this the final episode of our 4 part series on Muhal Richard Abrams and his collaboration with Bobby Zankel's Warriors of the Wonderful Sound, WRTI's J. Michael Harrison interviews Muhal as he relates some of his personal history and and what it has been like working with the Warriors. Muhal's composition will be performed live by Bobby and the Warriors at Montgomery County Community College on April 28, 2012.
